org.apache.accumulo.core.client.impl

Class AuthenticationTokenIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • TokenIdentifier
      • org.apache.accumulo.core.client.impl.AuthenticationTokenIdentifier

  • public class AuthenticationTokenIdentifier
extends TokenIdentifier
    Implementation that identifies the underlying Token for Accumulo.
Shall be called with DelegationTokenConfig, TAuthenticationTokenIdentifier, DelegationTokenImpl.
